-- Wataniya Insurance to Insure Saudi Cement’s Assets, Possessions
-- B y   W a e l   M a h d i
-- 2012-01-01T09:27:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-01/wataniya-insurance-to-insure-saudi-cement-s-assets-possessions.html
Saudi Cement Co. (SACCO) ,  Saudi Arabia ’s
second-largest cement producer by market value, awarded an
insurance contract to  Wataniya Insurance Co (WATAN) ., it said in a
statement to the Saudi bourse today.  Wataniya will start insuring Saudi Cement’s “assets and
possessions” starting from today, the cement-maker said. The
contract doesn’t include medical insurance, it said. The annual
insurance premium on the contract is estimated at 8 million
riyals ($2.1 million), Saudi Cement said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
